from heapq import heapify, heappush, heappop
from typing import *
def f_gold(apples: List[int], days: List[int]) -> int:
    q = []
    n = len(apples)
    i = ans = 0
    while i < n or q:
        if i < n and apples[i] > 0:
            heappush(q, [i + days[i] - 1, apples[i]])
        while q and q[0][0] < i:
            heappop(q)
        if q:
            end, num = heappop(q)
            num -= 1
            ans += 1
            if num > 0 and end > i:
                heappush(q, [end, num])
        i += 1
    return ans
